'''Benedict Taylor''' is an English actor who played [[Porro Dolphe]] (or Bravo 2) in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. His sister is [[Femi Taylor]], who played [[Oola]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']]. He also played the part of [[Wikipedia:Prince Sixtus of Bourbon-Parma|Prince Sixtus of Bourbon-Parma]] in an episode of [[George Lucas]]' TV series [[Wikipedia:The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles|''The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles'']].

